== Padr Agnelak Magnnem ==

'''Prayer to Father Agnel'''



Sorpodvedar Deva, amchea sorginchea Bapa, amche soddvonne khatir, Tuji manddavoll, dhinvaxi monan ami ollkhotanv ani teach khatir Tujea vinchun kaddloleam sevokam udexim ochoriam legun Tum korun dakhoitai mhonn mandtanv. Tujea Putachea panvlar ami koxem porim cholunk zai hem dakhounk, Tuzo visvaxi sevok Padr Agnel, ek nomunno koso amkam diloi mhonn Tuka dhinvastanv ani tujea Povitr Atmeachea uzvaddan, Padr Agnelachea bhagivont jivitachi dekh ami gheunk pavlear puro mhonn kallzant thaun magtanv. Toxench atam Padr Agnel, Tujea Putachea, Jezuchea onodbhorit jivitant, bhagidar zalo mhonn dakhounk ho upkar ( tuji goroz sang ) ek khunna koxi favo kor mhonn vinoitanv.

Bhagevontacho Man Mellunk Magnnem

Ogonnit kaklutichea Deva, sorpott poddun Tujeam paiam sorxim, ami magtanv vhodda visvasan, Tuji khuxi ani amchea boreponnak upkarta zalear, Padr Agnelak Santacho man favo kor, amchea Povitr Sobheche, Igorjeche, ughodd porghottnne udexim. Magtanv amchea Somia [[Jezu|Jezu Kristache]] nanvim. 


